        <h2 id='surf'>Surfing</h2>
        <h4 class='post'> October 17, 2020</h4>
        <p class='entry'> I surfed Ho'okipa this morning and it was really fun! The waves were 3-4 feet, and conditions were all time. I surfed the point for about 2 hours and caught a ton of good waves. Stoked! </p>
        <img src='https://www.kasandbox.org/programming-images/avatars/aqualine-sapling.png'>
        <h2 id='skate'>Skateboarding</h2>
         <h4 class='post'> October 5, 2020</h4>
         <p class='entry'> This evening I skated Lahaina Skatepark with a few of my friends. This is my favorite skatepark on the island, because of the design, and friendly crowd. I was stoked to land a few new tricks too! </p>
         <img src='https://www.kasandbox.org/programming-images/avatars/aqualine-seed.png'>
        <h2 id='boog'>Bodyboarding</h2>
         <h4 class='post'> October 10, 2020</h4>
         <p class='entry'> This morning I went down to big beach to bodyboard and skim. The waves were small but still really fun for bodyboarding. I got a few little barrels and a couple good flips while skimming. </p> 
